rom illegal brick kilns within three months. The directive includes restoring agricultural lands and water bodies. The tribunal also mandated the AP Pollution Control Board to levy compensation on operators for air quality deterioration and soil fertility loss, emphasizing strict regulation of such activities.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/ngt-orders-compensation-assessment-restoration-of-lands-affected-by-illegal-brick-kilns-in-ntr-district/132140414?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-279284/132140414.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}